# List Companion

```scalascript
val filled = List.fill(4)(0)
println(filled.mkString(", "))

val indexed = List.tabulate(5)(i => i * i)
println(indexed.mkString(", "))

val ranged = List.range(1, 6)
println(ranged.mkString(", "))

val stepped = List.range(0, 10, 3)
println(stepped.mkString(", "))
```
